description: Lightly seasoned skewers that are a must for BBQ's.
keywords: Skewer & kebab,Seafood free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Soy free,Wheat free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Chicken Skewers with Capsicum, Onions, Rosemary & Garlic Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 small red capsicum, deseeded and cut into chunks
1 small green capsicum, deseeded and cut into chunks
1 small white onion, peeled and cut into chunks
1 small red onion, peeled and cut into chunks

recipeInstructions.text: Heat up a chargrill to a medium heat. Add the plantbased chicken and vegetables onto skewers.
Chargrill the skewers for 10 minutes while rotating. Cut open the largest piece of chicken to ensure it is cooked through. If not, return to chargrill for another 4 minutes and repeat.
